SCP-4190:  A Twenty Thousand League Delay

Author:  Lt Flops
附加记录：    
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
Entry for DAY ONE  ◁
Entry for DAY TWO  ◁
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~

This is an SCP for the FINAL DAY  of the Uncle Nicolini gave me the motivation to continue writing.

Spelling Bee 

I coin a new term in this one: Ephialteic. Derived from the Greek . Ephialteic  is on the flipside of Oneiric .

Oneiric  = of or related to dreams.
Ephialteic  = of or related to nightmares.

